sequenceDiagram
    actor O as Operador (empleado/gerente)
    participant B as Browser (ventas.html)
    participant JS as app.js
    participant S as GestionDBServer
    participant V as Ventas.java
    participant DB as Oracle DB

    O->>B: Arma carrito + cliente + metodo pago
    B->>JS: checkout()
    JS->>S: POST /api/ventas {clientId,payment,employeeId,items,received}
    S->>V: post()

    V->>DB: BEGIN TX + buscar metodo_pago
    alt Metodo = Credito
        V->>DB: validar cliente con credito habilitado
    end

    loop Por cada item
        V->>DB: SELECT producto FOR UPDATE
        DB-->>V: precio y stock
        V->>V: valida stock y calcula subtotal
    end

    V->>DB: INSERT factura RETURNING idfactura
    V->>DB: INSERT detallefactura (batch)
    V->>DB: COMMIT
    V-->>JS: 200 {invoiceId,total,change}
    JS->>JS: limpia carrito y recarga ventas
    JS-->>B: muestra "Factura FAC-..."
